// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0623 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: acaff604-1fb4-5939-97d5-1a8bb541a977

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:23.04*")
